{
  "stem": "8895.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was-- I was 12 years old then.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was very hurt, because I saw my father suffering.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] He loved Germany.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He loved it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "All his roots were there, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But he was everywhere loved, everywhere.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "No matter where he was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I'm sure that he missed Germany.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was sure that can't go on longer than six weeks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Absolutely sure.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He said, we will be back in six weeks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I didn't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My-- my-- may parents-- [COUGHS] My Parents must have taken the decision, and didn't-- they didn't ask me or anything.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I went.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was-- there was no question or arguing or anything about it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Beg your pardon?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'33.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To Poland, to Katowice.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we stayed there till '39, just before the war.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Three days before the war, we fled to-- to the Russian border, because my-- my father said, if anything happens, then the Russians will be there.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't we didn't know that-- that-- we-- we-- we thought we can go back to Germany in no time.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We really did think so.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father thought so.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] He thought that can't last, because it was a crazy man.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "His speeches and all that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It is unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It wasn't-- it was a bit difficult, because every three months we had to get the new permission to live there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And sometimes we didn't get it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then we had a home in Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But everywhere-- it was everywhere very nice.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And Czechoslovakia was lovely.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We always had one room.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We all three slept together, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was-- wasn't-- but it wasn't-- that wasn't hardship, really.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know where the money came from, but-- I mean, there wasn't social services then.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
